@startuml
' --- Sơ đồ USE CASE TỔNG QUAN: 8 nhóm (G1–G8), ít dây — dễ đọc / dễ in ---
' Chi tiết UC1–UC34: use-case-clinic-management.puml

skinparam handwritten false
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 50
skinparam Padding 12
skinparam linetype polyline

title **Sơ đồ Use Case (tổng quan theo nhóm)**\n<size:10>Website đặt lịch & vận hành phòng khám — Medlatec</size>

left to right direction

skinparam usecase {
  FontSize 10
  FontStyle bold
  RoundCorner 14
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  BorderColor #F57C00
  FontColor #333333
  FontStyle bold
}
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #1565C0
  BorderThickness 2
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #37474F
  Thickness 1.2
}

actor "Bệnh nhân" as Patient
actor "Lễ tân" as Reception

rectangle "**Hệ thống Website**\n**đặt lịch & vận hành phòng khám**" as System {

  usecase "G1. Xác thực & tài khoản\n(UC1–UC3, UC34)" as G1 #E3F2FD
  usecase "G2. Hồ sơ bệnh nhân\n(UC4–UC8)" as G2 #E8F5E9
  usecase "G3. Lịch khám & quy trình khám\n(UC9–UC15, UC26–UC28, UC33, UC12–UC13)" as G3 #FFF3E0
  usecase "G4. Dịch vụ & giá\n(UC16, UC30)" as G4 #F3E5F5
  usecase "G5. Hóa đơn & thanh toán\n(UC17–UC19, UC29, UC31–UC32)" as G5 #E0F7FA
  usecase "G6. Nhắc lịch & báo cáo\n(UC20–UC22)" as G6 #FBE9E7
  usecase "G7. Chat nội bộ\n(UC23–UC24)" as G7 #ECEFF1
  usecase "G8. Dashboard\n(UC25)" as G8 #E8EAF6
}

actor "Bác sĩ" as Doctor
actor "Thu ngân" as Cashier
actor "Quản trị viên" as Admin

' Trái: Bệnh nhân, Lễ tân — nối Actor --- nhóm
Patient --- G1
Patient --- G3
Patient --- G4
Patient --- G5
Patient --- G6

Reception --- G1
Reception --- G2
Reception --- G3
Reception --- G4
Reception --- G7
Reception --- G8

' Phải: nhóm --- Actor (để actor nằm bên phải khung)
G1 --- Doctor
G2 --- Doctor
G3 --- Doctor
G7 --- Doctor

G1 --- Cashier
G5 --- Cashier
G6 --- Cashier
G7 --- Cashier
G8 --- Cashier

G1 --- Admin
G4 --- Admin
G5 --- Admin
G6 --- Admin
G8 --- Admin

note as N
  **Đọc nhanh:** mỗi ô **G1–G8** gom các UC trong ngoặc.
  Sơ đồ **chi tiết** (đủ oval & «include»/«extend»): **use-case-clinic-management.puml**
end note

@enduml
